stimulus:
Welcome to Interactive Stroop Test with SOA -- 2 Colors.

Press any key to begin.

You will see text in 2 colors which are individually assigned to a key.

  • Blue - key F
  • Red - key J

Your task is to press the key as soon as possible when you see a color.

For example, you should press F key when seeing a word in color Blue, even if the word is Red.

The experiment will start with a practice for you to be familiar with the task.

Then a test will start.

Press any key to begin the practice.

The test will start. Remember to press the key according to the color rather than the word.

You can press S if you do not catch the blink color.

Press any key to begin.
